Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: CAPD compiled package - development version.
 The CAPD library is a collection of flexible C++ modules which are mainly designed to computation of homology of sets and maps and nonrigorous and validated numerics for dynamical systems. See http://capd.ii.uj.edu.pl and http://redhom.ii.uj.edu.pl .


Package: capd
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description:  CAPD compiled package - runtime version.
 The CAPD library is a collection of flexible C++ modules which are mainly designed to computation of homology of sets and maps and nonrigorous and validated numerics for dynamical systems. See http://capd.ii.uj.edu.pl and http://redhom.ii.uj.edu.pl .
